question: What is the location of the Gyeongju City Hall in Gyeongju, South Korea?
asked_question_translated: Hvor ligger Gyeongju rådhus i Gyeongju, Sør-Korea?
answer: Gyeongju rådhus ligger i Hwangnam-dong, i Gyeongju, Sør-Korea.
answer_translated_eng: Gyeongju City Hall is located in Hwangnam-dong, in Gyeongju, South Korea.
